      <a href="/healthgood/" class="rli-cross-card"><i class="fas fa-heart-pulse"></i><span>健康促進</span><small>農民職業健康與傷病預防</small></a>
      <a href="/dignity-farming-initiative/" class="rli-cross-card"><i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i><span>尊嚴農業倡議</span><small>推動農業工作者勞動尊嚴</small></a>
      <a href="/research-result/" class="rli-cross-card"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i><span>研究成果</span><small>田野調查與學術研究產出</small></a>
